</li>
<li id="cite_note-Needham-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Needham_6-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation book">Tsien Tsuen-Hsuin; Joseph Needham (1985). <i>Paper and Printing</i>. Science and Civilisation in China. <b>5 part 1</b>. Cambridge University Press. p.&#160;158,201.</span></span></li>
