<li id="cite_note-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFIssawi1980">Issawi 1980</a>, pp.&#160;492; <a href="#CITEREFDuchesne2006">Duchesne 2006</a>, p.&#160;83</span></li>
