<li id="cite_note-49"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-49">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">The British Library <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.bl.uk/catalogues/istc/index.html">Incunabula Short Title Catalogue</a> gives 29,777 separate <i>editions</i> (not copies) as of 8 January 2008, which however includes some print items from the 16th century (retrieved 11.03.2010). According to Bettina Wagner: "Das Second-Life der Wiegendrucke. Die Inkunabelsammlung der Bayerischen Staatsbibliothek", in: Griebel, Rolf; Ceynowa, Klaus (eds.): "Information, Innovation, Inspiration. 450 Jahre Bayerische Staatsbibliothek", K G Saur, München 2008, <a href="Special_BookSources/9783598117725" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 978-3-598-11772-5</a>, pp. 207–224 (207f.), the <a href="Incunabula_Short_Title_Catalogue" title="Incunabula Short Title Catalogue">Incunabula Short Title Catalogue</a> lists 28,107 editions published before 1501.</span></li>
