<li>Hind, Arthur M., <i>An Introduction to a History of Woodcut</i>, Houghton Mifflin Co. 1935 (in USA), reprinted Dover Publications, 1963 <a href="Special_BookSources/0486209520" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-486-20952-0</a></li>
